        <h1>Spinach Tofu</h1>
       
        <div class="recipe-details">
         <img src="r8-st.jpeg" alt="Spinach Tofu" class="recipe-image">
            <div class="ingredients">
                <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>200g tofu, cubed</li>
                    <li>2 cups spinach, chopped</li>
                    <li>1 tbsp soy sauce</li>
                    <li>1 tbsp sesame oil</li>
                    <li>1 clove garlic, minced</li>
                    <li>Salt to taste</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="instructions">
                <h2>Instructions:</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Heat sesame oil in a pan over medium heat.</li>
                    <li>Add garlic and saute ½ until fragrant.</li>
                    <li>Add tofu and cook until golden brown.</li>
                    <li>Add spinach and soy sauce, cook until wilted.</li>
                    <li>Serve warm.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>

